    "en": {
      "title": "Risk of landslides in Kalutara, Kandy, Matale and Ratnapura",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the National Building Research Organization, there is a risk of landslides in four districts of the island due to the prevailing heavy rains.",
        "A spokesperson of the National Building Research Organization said that the risk of this landslide has emerged in the districts of Kalutara, Kandy, Matale and Ratnapura.",
        "The spokesman also mentioned that the people living in the hilly and sloping areas of those areas should be on the lookout for signs of landslides."
      ],
